{
    "id": "3dprinting/blob-of-death",
    "title": "Witness a Blob of Death",
    "description": "Skipping a first-layer check lets a failed Z homing extrude in mid-air, engulfing the nozzle in molten plastic.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/blob_of_death_nozzle_fail.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/sydney.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "You start a print and walk away. Without verifying the first layer, the Z axis mis-homes and the printer extrudes in mid-air.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "3dprint-blob-of-death",
                    "goto": "encased",
                    "text": "Skip the first-layer check anyway.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        { "id": "8aa6dc27-dc42-4622-ac88-cbd57f48625f", "count": 1 },
                        { "id": "d3590107-25ff-4de5-af3a-46e2497bfc52", "count": 10 },
                        { "id": "061fd221-404a-4bd1-9432-3e25b0f17a2c", "count": 100 }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "encased",
            "text": "Filament strings into cotton candy, then hardens into a molten helmet around the hotend.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "document-blob-of-death",
                    "goto": "salvage",
                    "text": "Power down, photograph the blob, and log the fail.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        { "id": "8896a0ef-edd8-4d19-ac14-19ee66470e54", "count": 1 },
                        { "id": "70bb8d86-2c4e-4330-9705-371891934686", "count": 1 }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "salvage",
            "text": "The hotend is entombed. Snip zip ties, warm the blob, and swap in a fresh nozzle while your goggles fog from the steam of regret.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "repair-blob-of-death",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "Cut away the glob and install a new nozzle.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        { "id": "8896a0ef-edd8-4d19-ac14-19ee66470e54", "count": 1 },
                        { "id": "fbecc523-fb93-4d00-be08-2ed9f53f158c", "count": 1 },
                        { "id": "c9b51052-4594-42d7-a723-82b815ab8cc2", "count": 1 },
                        { "id": "5029f7cb-3359-4153-b7ca-4b53988ac086", "count": 1 }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "The printer is clean again, the blob logged for posterity, and you promise to watch the next first layer like a hawk.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Lesson learned.",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        { "id": "8aa6dc27-dc42-4622-ac88-cbd57f48625f", "count": 1 },
                        { "id": "280ed361-ac70-4ab9-bcd9-aee481790faf", "count": 1 }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
    "rewards": [],
    "requiresQuests": ["3dprinter/start"]
}
